{"tid":1553750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"34歲的C朗是意甲本賽季衝刺速度最快的前鋒，34.62km/h","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T05:10:49.000Z","uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f4632f2142708f9cb92434670fb0d57a63b641","tid":1553750,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:52:59.000Z","msg":"據《米蘭體育報》報導，34歲的C羅是意甲本賽季衝刺速度最快的前鋒，34.62km/h。<br />\n<br />\n 該媒體還表示，這項數據放在意甲所有球員之中，也僅次於馬諾拉斯（35.41km/h）。 而在隊內，C羅的最快衝刺速度擊敗了道格拉斯-科斯塔、桑德羅以及達尼洛。<br />\n<br />\n 排在C羅後面的分別是都靈前鋒紮紮（34.56km/h）、羅馬後衛曼奇尼（34.46km/h）以及亞特蘭大後衛吉姆西蒂（34.26km/h）"},{"pid":"33390eea35e5705b4b73bb1293dfcb2973bc09ae","tid":1553750,"uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:54:23.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠美斯沖廁快?<br />\n<br />\n馬勒當拿再批美斯：賽前去20次廁所 如何做領袖.."},{"pid":"fd88e3117fbf17b316c4f4b7dde6744cf20fc850","tid":1553750,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"佩狗死全家"},{"pid":"2d74dc1c676d413316fa9c8ed04518f9245a82d6","tid":1553750,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33390eea35e5705b4b73bb1293dfcb2973bc09ae","tid":1553750,"uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:54:23.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠美斯沖廁快?<br />\n<br />\n馬勒當拿再批美斯：賽前去20次廁所 如何做領袖.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"屌你，又串我美球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b703f3acf6c7c791e54b32b202e71df2c13ca9","tid":1553750,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33390eea35e5705b4b73bb1293dfcb2973bc09ae","tid":1553750,"uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:54:23.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠美斯沖廁快?<br />\n<br />\n馬勒當拿再批美斯：賽前去20次廁所 如何做領袖.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\